# Login
POST - http://localhost:8000/auth/token
	request body:
  ```
	{
		"username": "faysalstat04@gmail.com",
		"password": "admin"
	}
```
# Validate the Token
GET - http://localhost:8000/auth/validate
	request param:

Param name: token
Param value: Collect the token from Login response.

